A global layout wrapper with a slot, navigation, footer, and clean structure.

```astro
---
import NavBar from './NavBar.astro';
import Footer from './Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>GitDigital Products</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/global.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <NavBar />

    <main class="container">
      <slot />
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }
</style>
```

